{
  "text": "In this previously sedentary cohort it is also possible that our subjects were less active than previously outside the training times. We did not make any specific measurements of overall physical activity in the current study and we think it unlikely that this could have been reduced. While devices are being developed to measure physical activity continuously over several days [CITATION_1] , we did not use these in our study.",
  "correct_citation": {
    "[CITATION_1]": "22445969"
